| ------------ | ---------: |
| ESP32        |       ₹500 |
| Sensors      |       ₹200 |
| LED Driver   |       ₹300 |
| Power Supply |       ₹200 |
| Total        |      ₹1200 |

2. Smart Parking Availability System
Objective

Provide real-time information about available parking spaces and reduce traffic congestion caused by searching for parking.

Sensors Required
Ultrasonic sensor (HC-SR04) for vehicle detection
IR sensor for parking slot monitoring
Hardware
ESP32
Ultrasonic sensors
LED indicators
Wi-Fi module
Connectivity
Wi-Fi / LoRa
HTTP REST API or MQTT

DATA FLOW :
Parking Sensor Nodes
          |
          ↓
        ESP32
          |
       MQTT/HTTP
          |
          ↓
       Cloud Database
          |
          ↓
 Mobile Parking App

Working

Each parking slot has a sensor. When a vehicle occupies a slot, the sensor updates the cloud database.
Users can view available parking spaces through a mobile application.

