| ----------------- | ---------: |
| ESP32             |       ₹500 |
| Ultrasonic Sensor |       ₹150 |
| LED Indicator     |        ₹50 |
| Enclosure         |       ₹200 |
| Total             |       ₹900 |

3. Smart Air Quality Monitoring System
Objective

Monitor pollution levels in Jammu and provide alerts during poor air quality conditions.

Sensors Required
MQ-135 gas sensor for air quality
PM2.5 sensor
DHT11 temperature and humidity sensor
Hardware
ESP32
MQ-135
PMS5003 particulate sensor
DHT11
Connectivity
LoRaWAN for long-distance communication
MQTT for cloud publishing

Data Flow :
Air Quality Sensors
          |
          ↓
        ESP32
          |
        LoRa
          |
          ↓
     IoT Gateway
          |
        MQTT
          |
          ↓
        Cloud
          |
          ↓
 Dashboard / Alerts
Working

Sensors continuously measure pollutants and environmental conditions.
If pollution exceeds safe limits, the dashboard generates alerts for authorities and citizens.

